    <item>
      <title>大众汽车交付量因中国市场低迷和电动汽车市场困境而下降</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-14/volkswagen-deliveries-fall-on-china-slump-and-ev-struggles</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于电动汽车需求疲软以及主要中国市场的激烈竞争拖累了销售，大众汽车集团去年的汽车交付量有所下降。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-14/volkswagen-deliveries-fall-on-china-slump-and-ev-struggles</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 14 Jan 2025 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>经济学家告诉 Ifo，全球通胀将在未来数年维持高位</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-14/global-inflation-will-remain-high-for-years-economists-tell-ifo</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一项新调查显示，经济学家预计全球通胀至少在 2028 年之前仍将维持高位，这可能会加剧市场对持续价格压力的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-14/global-inflation-will-remain-high-for-years-economists-tell-ifo</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 14 Jan 2025 09:59:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
